            <title><![CDATA[【🎧耳机发烧友快看！#经常用耳机的3个60原则#】今天是第25个全国爱耳日，据世卫组织，个人音频设备音量过大、长时间佩戴耳机是造成听力损失风险的重要因素。...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【🎧耳机发烧友快看！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%BA%E7%9A%843%E4%B8%AA60%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%BA%E7%9A%843%E4%B8%AA60%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#经常用耳机的3个60原则#</span></a>】今天是第25个全国爱耳日，据世卫组织，个人音频设备音量过大、长时间佩戴耳机是造成听力损失风险的重要因素。医务人员建议：①环境本底噪声分贝不超过60分贝以上；②耳机音量小于它的60%；③<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%8760%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%8760%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#耳机使用时间不要超过60分钟#</span></a> 👇🏻<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5007756235571224" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">人民日报的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/0033ImPzly1hndhzb690nj60zk0k041m02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/qkwq2jXBlx08cZji5R2w01041200eSxP0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709586737&amp;ssig=8fmJZMGKVi&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/3FUTUW4Plx08cZjhx4Gs010412007fCO0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709586737&amp;ssig=0XXoVOqapj&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/BCjWSPyYlx08cZjhy1du010412004lw90E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709586737&amp;ssig=upPrj%2Bc0zD&